921
01:16:10,043 --> 01:16:10,783
Baik.

922
01:16:10,957 --> 01:16:12,263
Jesse, belok kiri.

923
01:16:12,437 --> 01:16:13,501
Mari berondong orang ini.

924
01:16:13,525 --> 01:16:14,570
Dimengerti!

925
01:16:16,963 --> 01:16:18,225
Selamat berburu.

926
01:16:18,399 --> 01:16:19,575
Ini waktunya Bo.

