Mayday, Iroquois, 201.

1225
01:47:33,098 --> 01:47:36,275
Pelacak Radio. Ada satu,
kemungkinan dua pilot jatuh.

1226
01:47:36,450 --> 01:47:37,799
Meminta bantuan segera.

1227
01:47:37,973 --> 01:47:39,994
